Comment: There are co-workers who do their best to make this place feel like home for clients and fellow co-workers. Often in this field, constant encouragement and attention to detail is important on all levels of managements.  Its very uplifting to see co-workers come together for a common goal.  Management is very supportive in most times of need.  In general, most people that walk through the doors are here to make a positive impact in each other's lives. I am very appreciative of all I have learned and the ways I have been helpful to those around me.  I would absolutely recommend this company to anyone who has a passion for helping people.
